Items.mt: <[>Dafu uncle's time to cast the sword is untimely, and the two disciples of the Sword Blade School and the Flying White School, both of them commissioned to cast the sword at noon. The next step is to continue the investigation, or to tell who was the first to commission the sword casting? <]>
